NAME
    Hash::DefHash::Normalize - Normalize DefHash

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.040 of Hash::DefHash::Normalize (from
    Perl distribution Hash-DefHash-Normalize), released on 2018-09-10.

SYNOPSIS
     use Hash::DefHash::Normalize qw(normalize_defhash);

     my $ndh = normalize_defhash($dh);

FUNCTIONS
  normalize_defhash($dh[, \%opts ]) => HASH
    Normalize and check DefHash $dh (a hashref). Return normalized hash,
    which is a shallow copy of $dh. Die on error.

    Available options:

    *   remove_internal_properties => BOOL (default: 0)

        If set to 1, all properties and attributes starting with underscore
        ("_") with will be stripped. According to DefHash specification,
        they are ignored and usually contain notes/comments/extra
        information.

